Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad5\fad(0,500)\bord0\fs60\t(0,3400,\fs16)\move(223,224,242,188,0,3341)}{t(0,0,\\c&H000001&\t(500,4000,\c&H4D4E4F&)}第二季 第二十二集
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,《綠箭俠》前情回顧\N{\b0\fs12}Previously, on "Arrow"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.41,0:00:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚我們齊心協力\N{\b0\fs12}Tonight we rise up as one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.52,0:00:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,奪回這座城市\N{\b0\fs12}and take back this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德還有二十個跟他一樣的人\N{\b0\fs12}Slade's got 20 guys just like him,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.20,0:00:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我們沒辦法阻止他\N{\b0\fs12}and we have no way to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.71,0:00:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,米拉庫魯  我們要用它製造解藥\N{\b0\fs12}Mirakuru. We're going to use it to make a cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.90,0:00:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德承諾讓我當市長\N{\b0\fs12}Slade promised me city hall,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他兌現了這個承諾\N{\b0\fs12}and he delivered.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.29,0:00:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他也向你作出過承諾\N{\b0\fs12}I understand he made you a promise, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.26,0:00:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這件事結束之前  還有一個人必須得死\N{\b0\fs12}There is still one person who has to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.07,0:00:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他們人太多了  我們打不過\N{\b0\fs12}There's so many of them! We can't fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.39,0:00:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要\N{\b0\fs12}We're not going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.21,0:01:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.27,0:01:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.78,0:01:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你殺了我\N{\b0\fs12}You killed me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.86,0:01:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我來還你一個人情\N{\b0\fs12}let me return the favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.37,0:01:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你殺不了我\N{\b0\fs12}You can't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.69,0:01:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你並非不可戰勝\N{\b0\fs12}You're not invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.86,0:01:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多了\N{\b0\fs12}Close enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.50,0:01:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.77,0:01:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你還好嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.57,0:01:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,隧道塌了\N{\b0\fs12}The tunnel collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.61,0:01:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我被困住了\N{\b0\fs12}I'm trapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.97,0:01:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是\N{\b0\fs12}I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.09,0:01:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,越來越\N{\b0\fs12}It's getting really...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.59,0:01:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,難以呼吸了\N{\b0\fs12}hard to breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你會沒事的\N{\b0\fs12}You are going to be OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.95,0:01:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,把你能看見的東西都告訴我\N{\b0\fs12}I need you to tell me everything that you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.12,0:01:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,石頭  水  還有\N{\b0\fs12}Rocks, and water, and--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,還有你的弓\N{\b0\fs12}and your bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.26,0:02:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,看到我的箭袋了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}You see my quiver?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.37,0:02:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  是的  我拿到了\N{\b0\fs12}Wait! Yeah, yes, I have it! I have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.11,0:02:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,裡面還有多少支箭\N{\b0\fs12}How many arrows are in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.26,0:02:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,有好幾支\N{\b0\fs12}There's a bunch of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.15,0:02:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,裡面應該有一支箭是金屬箭頭\N{\b0\fs12}There should be one with a metallic head
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.70,0:02:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,比其它箭頭都大\N{\b0\fs12}that's bigger than the rest of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.27,0:02:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Do you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.06,0:02:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這個有什麼用\N{\b0\fs12}Why do I need this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.31,0:02:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,因為這個是爆破箭頭\N{\b0\fs12}Because it's an explosive arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.74,0:02:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你得用它\N{\b0\fs12}And you're going to fire it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.60,0:02:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你能幫我省點時間和精力嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Do you want to save me some time and energy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴我費利西蒂•斯莫克在哪裡\N{\b0\fs12}Then tell me where I can find Felicity Smoak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.05,0:02:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,從那時候起  我一直很想朝她那張\N{\b0\fs12}I have been aching to put a bullet
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.92,0:02:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,自以為是的小臉上開一槍\N{\b0\fs12}in her smug little face ever since the day...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.16,0:02:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為氣囊要彈出來呢\N{\b0\fs12}I really thought the airbags were going to go off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝幫忙\N{\b0\fs12}Thanks for the help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.11,0:03:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,有奧利弗的消息嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Any word from Oliver?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.69,0:03:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,狄格\N{\b0\fs12}Dig...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你想怎麼做  再撞她一下嗎\N{\b0\fs12}What do you think, hit her again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,快開  快開\N{\b0\fs12}Go, go, go, go, go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}武器室\N未經允許  禁止入內
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,出去  出去\N{\b0\fs12}Get out! Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}市政廳\N市長辦公室  星城中心區地檢署
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.13,0:04:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,全城的記者都在趕來\N{\b0\fs12}Reports are coming in from all over the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.63,0:04:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,星城總院正在準備接收傷者\N{\b0\fs12}Starling General is preparing for possible casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,軍隊已經從港灣大道南部出發了\N{\b0\fs12}Power is out south of Harbor Boulevard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.88,0:04:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,州長  州長\N{\b0\fs12}Governor. Governor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這種時候派出國民警衛隊\N{\b0\fs12}Sending in the national guard at this point
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.13,0:04:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,只會造成更大的恐慌\N{\b0\fs12}will only cause mass hysteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.36,0:04:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,請相信我和我的員警\N{\b0\fs12}Trust me and my police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.69,0:04:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我們能夠控制局面\N{\b0\fs12}We have this situation under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-市長先生  -斯賓塞地檢官\N{\b0\fs12}- Mr. Mayor. - D.A. Spencer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,發生了什麼事\N{\b0\fs12}What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,有一群帶面具的人在城市裡到處破壞\N{\b0\fs12}There are men in masks tearing through the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我知道  我們正在努力控制局面\N{\b0\fs12}Yes, I know. And we're doing everything we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.09,0:04:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}星城一片混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.93,0:04:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,星城警署的警力已經全部出動\N{\b0\fs12}The SCPD have already mobilized.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不  那些員警處理不了這種情況\N{\b0\fs12}No, the police force, they're not equipped to handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你不明白\N{\b0\fs12}You don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.33,0:04:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我從來沒見過這種狀況\N{\b0\fs12}I have never seen anything like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這些  戴面具的人\N{\b0\fs12}These--the men in masks,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,簡直  簡直就不是人類\N{\b0\fs12}It--it's like they're not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不是人類\N{\b0\fs12}Not human?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.34,0:04:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,凱特  你知道你在說什麼嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Kate, do you even hear yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.67,0:04:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,聽著  我知道你很害怕\N{\b0\fs12}Look, I know you're scared,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但你得冷靜下來\N{\b0\fs12}But you need to pull yourself together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:05:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,星城需要我們兩個都能冷靜思考\N{\b0\fs12}Starling City needs both of us thinking clearly right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼你這麼冷靜\N{\b0\fs12}How are you so calm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}星城一片混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我知道我們能夠度過這一關\N{\b0\fs12}Because I know we're going to get through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,當我們挺過來以後\N{\b0\fs12}And when we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,星城會比以往更強大更美好\N{\b0\fs12}Starling City will be stronger and better for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.61,0:05:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我能依靠你嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Can I count on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你和我攜手作戰\N{\b0\fs12}I need you with me on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\b0\fs12}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.99,0:05:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼讓我們一起拯救城市\N{\b0\fs12}Then let's save the city together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}星城一片混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你離爆破點夠遠了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Are you far enough away from the debris to avoid the blast?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\b0\fs12}I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我射不了那麼遠呢\N{\b0\fs12}What if I can't shoot that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那把弓是復合材質的  勞蕾爾\N{\b0\fs12}The bow's a hybrid compound, Laurel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.22,0:05:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,它完全能夠做到\N{\b0\fs12}It's going to do all the work for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要做的只是\N{\b0\fs12}All I need you to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.68,0:05:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,瞄準瓦礫的正中間\N{\b0\fs12}just aim at the middle of the debris.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.93,0:05:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,深呼吸\N{\b0\fs12}Take a deep breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,重心放在兩腳之間\N{\b0\fs12}Center your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,左手握住弓\N{\b0\fs12}Left hand on the bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.82,0:05:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,把箭放到弓弦上\N{\b0\fs12}Place the arrow on the drawstring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.39,0:05:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我能行  我能行\N{\b0\fs12}OK, OK, OK, OK, OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:05:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  現在\N{\b0\fs12}All right, I want you to pull back
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,拉開弓弦\N{\b0\fs12}on the drawstring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,左臂伸直\N{\b0\fs12}And keep your left arm straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.45,0:06:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,行了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,數到三\N{\b0\fs12}You count to three
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,然後放箭的\N{\b0\fs12}and then you just let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.00,0:06:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你能做到\N{\b0\fs12}You can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.61,0:06:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,1  2\N{\b0\fs12}1, 2...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.12,0:06:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,3\N{\b0\fs12}3!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.87,0:06:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,射得漂亮\N{\b0\fs12}Nice shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,狄格爾  能聽見嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Diggle, you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.19,0:06:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  奧利弗  我們聽到了\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, Oliver, we hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.01,0:06:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要出來了\N{\b0\fs12}We're coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉不見了\N{\b0\fs12}Sara's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是被斯萊德抓走的\N{\b0\fs12}Slade must have taken her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.27,0:07:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,該死[俄語]\N{\b0\fs12}Chert.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是聲納  我在監視亞馬遜號\N{\b0\fs12}It's sonar. I was monitoring the "Amazo".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,她在移動\N{\b0\fs12}She's moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我們還剩一個魚雷  是吧\N{\b0\fs12}We have one torpedo left, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\b0\fs12}Da.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你能讓它沿直線射出去嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Could you rig it to fire in a straight line?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我在探索我究竟能做多少\N{\b0\fs12}I'm discovering capacity to do many things
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.87,0:07:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我從未想過能做的事\N{\b0\fs12}I never thought I would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.69,0:07:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你盡可能將潛艇靠近貨船\N{\b0\fs12}I need you to get the sub close enough to the freighter
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣我能遊過去\N{\b0\fs12}so that I can swim over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那你需要魚雷做什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Well, then, what do you need torpedo for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.37,0:07:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,如果一個小時內我和莎拉還沒回來\N{\b0\fs12}If Sara and I aren't back in an hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你就要擊沉亞馬遜號\N{\b0\fs12}you're going to sink the "Amazo".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不許動\N{\b0\fs12}Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你是誰\N{\b0\fs12}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.23,0:08:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我是她爸爸\N{\b0\fs12}I'm her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.63,0:08:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\b0\fs12}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.47,0:08:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾  感謝上帝\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel, thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.59,0:08:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧\N{\b0\fs12}Are you safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,現在沒事了\N{\b0\fs12}I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在和綠箭俠在一起\N{\b0\fs12}I'm with the Arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那  那就好\N{\b0\fs12}Well, that's-- that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,聽著  我想他還有事要去處理\N{\b0\fs12}Now listen, something tells me he's got work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:09:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-我要你避開大路  -好的\N{\b0\fs12}- I want you off the streets. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾  一定要保持低調 \N{\b0\fs12}Laurel, please, keep low,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,避人耳目  好嗎\N{\b0\fs12}keep out of sight, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.32,0:09:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸  我知道了  你不必  擔心我\N{\b0\fs12}Dad, I know, you don't have to worry...about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-你沒事吧  -沒事\N{\b0\fs12}- You OK?  - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.77,0:09:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢\N{\b0\fs12}You?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莎貝爾襲擊了狄格\N{\b0\fs12}Isabel attacked dig
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我用麵包車撞了她\N{\b0\fs12}so I hit her with the van.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是斯萊德的軍隊\N{\b0\fs12}Slade's army.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他至少派出了五十個和他一樣的人\N{\b0\fs12}He has at least 50 men out there, all like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他們無處不在\N{\b0\fs12}They're everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.82,0:09:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要阻止他們\N{\b0\fs12}We need to stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.72,0:09:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能有辦法\N{\b0\fs12}We might have a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.76,0:09:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,尖端科技研究實驗室打來電話\N{\b0\fs12}S.T.A.R. Labs called.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他們有解藥了  傳遞員已經在路上了\N{\b0\fs12}They have a cure. There's a courier en route.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.37,0:09:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,到哪了\N{\b0\fs12}Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.11,0:09:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}尖端科技研究實驗室
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.67,0:09:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}費利西蒂\N來電
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\b0\fs12}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我是費利西蒂•斯莫克  你在哪裡\N{\b0\fs12}Hey, it's Felicity Smoak. Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.92,0:09:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我想是在第四大街  我不知道發生了什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Fourth street, I think. I don't know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,突然冒出一個戴曲棍球面罩的人\N{\b0\fs12}A guy in a hockey mask came out of nowhere
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,襲擊了我的卡車\N{\b0\fs12}and attacked my truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.40,0:10:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-請救救我  -在那裡等著\N{\b0\fs12}- Please help me. - Stay where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我想動也動不了\N{\b0\fs12}I can't move even if I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.60,0:10:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得我腿斷了\N{\b0\fs12}I think my leg's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你該去了\N{\b0\fs12}You should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾  我不會半途拋下你走的\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel, I'm not leaving you out here in the middle of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我去警局  是往另一個方向走的\N{\b0\fs12}The precinct, it's in the other direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我會沒事的\N{\b0\fs12}I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.68,0:10:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\b0\fs12}no.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在不需要你\N{\b0\fs12}I don't need you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但其他人需要你\N{\b0\fs12}Everyone else does.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.77,0:10:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧\N{\b0\fs12}So go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,去拯救這個城市\N{\b0\fs12}Go save the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  你還在嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Hey! You still there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我在  我已經標記了你的電話\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, I'm here. I pinged your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我們來了\N{\b0\fs12}On our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,請快點\N{\b0\fs12}Please hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,找到他\N{\b0\fs12}Find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,在過去五分鐘裡\N{\b0\fs12}In the last five minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,星城警署收到超過200份\N{\b0\fs12}SCPD has had over 200 reports
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:10:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,面具男襲擊城市的報告\N{\b0\fs12}of masked men attacking the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我應該和勞蕾爾一起去\N{\b0\fs12}Should have gone with Laurel
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,確保她能夠到達警局\N{\b0\fs12}and made sure she got to the precinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,她會和她爸爸在一起的  不會有事的\N{\b0\fs12}She'll be with her father, she'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗  她不會有事的\N{\b0\fs12}She will, Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\b0\fs12}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我們離貨船十米遠\N{\b0\fs12}We are 10 meters away from the freighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.55,0:11:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但這還是太瘋狂了[俄語]\N{\b0\fs12}But still, this is sumasshedshiy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,太瘋狂了  你都不確定她是否在威爾遜那\N{\b0\fs12}Crazy. You cannot even be certain that Wilson has her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,阿納托利  你是個好人\N{\b0\fs12}You're a good man, Anatoly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.09,0:11:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,如果這是永別  那麼請多保重\N{\b0\fs12}If this is good-bye, be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我會很快再見到你和莎拉的\N{\b0\fs12}I will see you soon. You and Sara.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.45,0:11:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我說過了\N{\b0\fs12}I meant what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.49,0:11:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我們一個小時內沒回來\N{\b0\fs12}If we're not back in an hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你就擊沉貨船然後自己回家\N{\b0\fs12}you sink the freighter and get yourself home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.43,0:11:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得我可能更喜歡回巴哈馬\N{\b0\fs12}I think maybe I prefer Bahamas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.11,0:11:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道我們能否再見\N{\b0\fs12}I don't know if we will see each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但你要知道咱倆是永遠的朋友\N{\b0\fs12}But know that you have made friend for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你有什麼需要  無論是什麼\N{\b0\fs12}If there is anything you need, it does not matter what...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:11:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你盡管開口\N{\b0\fs12}you have only to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.11,0:12:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,保重[俄語]  我的朋友\N{\b0\fs12}Prochnost, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.09,0:12:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,包 包重\N{\b0\fs12}Proch...prochnost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.26,0:12:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,保重  保  我還要教你俄語\N{\b0\fs12}Prochnost...proch... I also teach you to speak Russian.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,聽著  我們要在\N{\b0\fs12}Listen up. We're going to establish a perimeter
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.69,0:12:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,第五大街和亞當斯街交匯點\N{\b0\fs12}with check-points at 5th and Adams,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,第二大街和金斯利街交匯點設立檢查站\N{\b0\fs12}2nd and Kingsley.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.75,0:12:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我們得創建一個安全區  聽懂了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}We got to create a safe zone, you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.14,0:12:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這些人到底是誰\N{\b0\fs12}Who the hell are these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.54,0:12:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這些人是敵人\N{\b0\fs12}These guys are the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他們肆意傷害無辜群眾\N{\b0\fs12}They're attacking innocents at random,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,到處襲擊  引發混亂\N{\b0\fs12}creating mayhem and chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要去幹掉他們\N{\b0\fs12}We need to put them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-副隊  -現在就去\N{\b0\fs12}- Lieutenant... - Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,聽我說  你見過這些人嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Listen to me, these guys, have you seen them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你見過他們嗎  他們是幹不掉的\N{\b0\fs12}You seen these guys? They do not go down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我們得叫來國民警衛隊\N{\b0\fs12}We got to call in the National Guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那是市長的工作\N{\b0\fs12}That's a call for the Mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他還沒有這麼做\N{\b0\fs12}And he hasn't made that yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.63,0:12:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他不會這麼做的\N{\b0\fs12}And he won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這次事件是布拉德市長發起的\N{\b0\fs12}Mayor Blood let this happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.27,0:12:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-什麼  -相信我\N{\b0\fs12}- What? - Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.43,0:12:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,幕後主使是布拉德\N{\b0\fs12}Blood's behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,即使我相信你\N{\b0\fs12}Look, even if I believe you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒那麼大權力\N{\b0\fs12}I don't have that kind of authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.94,0:12:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,在緊急情況下  警察局長有這個權力\N{\b0\fs12}Well, in an emergency, the chief of police does,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,快聯繫他\N{\b0\fs12}so get him on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.62,0:12:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,局長死了\N{\b0\fs12}Chief's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.47,0:13:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的話\N{\b0\fs12}Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.37,0:13:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一個人可以幫我們了\N{\b0\fs12}there's only one more guy we can call.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但你不會喜歡的\N{\b0\fs12}You're not going to like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,治安維持者\N{\b0\fs12}The vigilante.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,綠箭俠\N{\b0\fs12}The Arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,副隊\N{\b0\fs12}Lieutenant,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他違反了法律\N{\b0\fs12}I know he's breaking the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但我們現在面對的局面\N{\b0\fs12}But what we're up against,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,已經不是違法問題了  這關乎生死存亡\N{\b0\fs12}it's not about the law. It's about survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,現在一群蒙面人肆意踐踏我們的城市\N{\b0\fs12}We got masks tearing our city to pieces,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我們需要另一個蒙面人來阻止他們\N{\b0\fs12}and we're going to need a mask to stop 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,聯繫他吧\N{\b0\fs12}Make the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那好\N{\b0\fs12}Ok, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,還有件事\N{\b0\fs12}One more thing--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,對眼下的局面  你比我所有手下瞭解得都多\N{\b0\fs12}You know more about what's going on over everyone else I got.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我把決策權交給你  你來指揮這些人\N{\b0\fs12}I need you making decisions and leading these men...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.02,0:13:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,警探\N{\b0\fs12}Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.83,0:14:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我來  我帶你去安全的地方\N{\b0\fs12}Follow me. I can get you to safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.89,0:14:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉\N{\b0\fs12}Sara...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我們派駐街頭的記者已經失去聯繫\N{\b0\fs12}We lost contact with our reporter on the streets,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}市政廳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.21,0:14:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但已經有數十名目擊者證實這群蒙面人\N{\b0\fs12}but we have over two dozen confirmed sightings of masked men
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.92,0:14:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,在市內多個地點大肆破壞\N{\b0\fs12}attacking numerous municipal locations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,官方要求觀眾朋友盡量待在室內\N{\b0\fs12}Officials are asking that you stay indoors...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\b0\fs12}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.11,0:14:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-住手  -別  不要\N{\b0\fs12}- Stop! - No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:14:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了\N{\b0\fs12}Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,計劃不是這樣的\N{\b0\fs12}This isn't part of the plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,塞巴斯蒂安\N{\b0\fs12}Sebastian?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.49,0:15:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我是星城市長\N{\b0\fs12}I am mayor of Starling City,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我命令你立即放開她\N{\b0\fs12}and I order you to let her go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.85,0:15:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我不聽命於你\N{\b0\fs12}I don't take orders from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.30,0:15:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了\N{\b0\fs12}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有西婭的消息嗎  她安全嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Any word from Thea? Is she safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.38,0:15:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,在星城被襲之前\N{\b0\fs12}She decided to leave Starling
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.81,0:15:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,她就決定離開這裡了\N{\b0\fs12}before the attacks started.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.26,0:15:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,離大橋  還有運送人員不到兩英里了\N{\b0\fs12}Just under two miles to the bridge. And the courier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,打給你的\N{\b0\fs12}It's for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  警探\N{\b0\fs12}What is it, Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-需要我們做什麼  -我們\N{\b0\fs12}- How can we help you? - We?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,星城所有員警力量\N{\b0\fs12}The Starling City Police Force
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,將全力協助你應對這場危機\N{\b0\fs12}is standing with you on this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你們協助遏制這些蒙面人\N{\b0\fs12}We need help containing the soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.08,0:15:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我們正在想辦法\N{\b0\fs12}We're working something
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,阻止他們  但我們需要更多時間\N{\b0\fs12}and it may stop them but we need more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:16:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,交給我們  不管你打算做什麼  祝你好運\N{\b0\fs12}We can do that. Whatever you're doing, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.59,0:16:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,祝我們所有人好運\N{\b0\fs12}For all our sakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,想開上橋去只能走這條路\N{\b0\fs12}This is the only street that feeds into the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.40,0:16:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,全速沖過去\N{\b0\fs12}Floor it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.84,0:16:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,小心\N{\b0\fs12}Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.83,0:16:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,狄格\N{\b0\fs12}Dig?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:16:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,狄格爾\N{\b0\fs12}Diggle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.11,0:16:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我在這\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,她還有呼吸嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Is she breathing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-費利西蒂  -她還有呼吸\N{\b0\fs12}- Felicity! - Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我們得抓緊離開\N{\b0\fs12}Then we have to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,明白\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, I'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.51,0:18:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭\N{\b0\fs12}Thea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是來傷害你的\N{\b0\fs12}I'm not here to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.93,0:18:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我憑什麼相信你\N{\b0\fs12}Why should I believe you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.05,0:18:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你是個殺人犯\N{\b0\fs12}You're a murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.47,0:18:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是個恐怖分子  還是個瘋子\N{\b0\fs12}Terrorist, and psychopath!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我並不指望你能理解我的所作所為\N{\b0\fs12}I don't expect you to understand what I've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,現在不會\N{\b0\fs12}Not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.67,0:18:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我需要更多時間解釋\N{\b0\fs12}Not without more time to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.47,0:18:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼可能還活著\N{\b0\fs12}How are you even alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你來幹什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Why are here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽說了你母親的事\N{\b0\fs12}I heard what happened to your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.79,0:18:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要來確保你的安全\N{\b0\fs12}I needed to make sure you were all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.22,0:18:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要見到我的女兒\N{\b0\fs12}I needed to see my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.73,0:18:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是你的女兒\N{\b0\fs12}I am not your daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,對我你什麼都不是\N{\b0\fs12}You're nothing to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全不需要你\N{\b0\fs12}And I want nothing from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你聽明白了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,明白  但現在\N{\b0\fs12}Yes. But right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要我的幫助\N{\b0\fs12}you need my help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.38,0:18:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,需要我的保護\N{\b0\fs12}My protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.71,0:18:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你完全不知道現在外面有多危險  西婭\N{\b0\fs12}You have no idea, Thea, how dangerous it is out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.42,0:19:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,城市正在崩潰  讓我帶你去安全的地方吧\N{\b0\fs12}The city is falling. At least let me take you to safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.31,0:19:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,傳說暴君尼祿\N{\b0\fs12}They say Nero sang
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.69,0:19:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,對著一片火海的羅馬城高聲歡歌\N{\b0\fs12}as he watched Rome burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.94,0:19:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,現在我明白他的感受了\N{\b0\fs12}Now I understand why.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,要是莎朵能親眼看到這一切就好了\N{\b0\fs12}If only Shado were here to witness this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.61,0:19:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,莎朵是誰\N{\b0\fs12}Who's Shado?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是怎麼回事\N{\b0\fs12}What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你手下有個打了藥的\N{\b0\fs12}Once of your juiced-up
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,神經病殺手殺了我辦公室裡的所有人\N{\b0\fs12}jack boots just killed my entire office staff,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,還扭斷了地區檢察官的脖子\N{\b0\fs12}and snapped the district attorney's neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-然後呢  -然後\N{\b0\fs12}- And? - And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.84,0:19:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我們之前可不是這麼說的\N{\b0\fs12}And I never agreed to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.46,0:19:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你本來應該叫你的人收手的\N{\b0\fs12}You were supposed to call off your dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.16,0:19:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那是你的計劃  布拉德先生  不是我的\N{\b0\fs12}That was your plan, Mr. Blood, not mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我們有協議\N{\b0\fs12}We had a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你是擔心我不能履行約定嗎\N{\b0\fs12}And do you feel that I've not lived up to my end of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,外面死傷慘重的\N{\b0\fs12}Those are innocent people,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,都是無辜的平民\N{\b0\fs12}dying out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.88,0:20:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒必要連他們也殺\N{\b0\fs12}You do not need to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,當然有必要\N{\b0\fs12}Yes, I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾對一個人立下重誓\N{\b0\fs12}I made a promise to someone once,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,而我言出必踐\N{\b0\fs12}and I will uphold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.21,0:20:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你籌劃這一切\N{\b0\fs12}So this really is all about you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,真的只是為了傷害奧利弗•奎恩\N{\b0\fs12}just trying to hurt Oliver Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.46,0:20:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾對他發誓\N{\b0\fs12}I vowed to him
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.42,0:20:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我會奪走他珍視的一切東西\N{\b0\fs12}that I would take away everything
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.68,0:20:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,殺死所有他愛的人\N{\b0\fs12}and everyone he loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.16,0:20:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,而他愛這座城市\N{\b0\fs12}And he loves this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.81,0:20:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但這座城市\N{\b0\fs12}But this city...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.40,0:20:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,也是我的城市\N{\b0\fs12}It's mine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.37,0:20:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不再是了\N{\b0\fs12}Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,到了明天晚上\N{\b0\fs12}As of tomorrow night,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡就只剩下碎石  灰燼和死亡\N{\b0\fs12}it'll be nothing but rubble, ash, and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.65,0:20:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,到時候這裡將變成再好不過的\N{\b0\fs12}A land only good for one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,墳墓\N{\b0\fs12}Graves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉\N{\b0\fs12}Sara...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.26,0:21:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪裡了\N{\b0\fs12}Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這不重要\N{\b0\fs12}Doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼回來\N{\b0\fs12}Why did you come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.52,0:21:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\b0\fs12}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.20,0:21:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡沒有屬於我的東西\N{\b0\fs12}There isn't anything here for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你的家在這裡\N{\b0\fs12}Your family's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾  你不瞭解我\N{\b0\fs12}You don't know, Laurel, about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.94,0:21:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道我是誰  我變成了什麼樣子\N{\b0\fs12}About who I am and who I've become.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.19,0:21:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我只知道你是個英雄\N{\b0\fs12}I know you're a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.10,0:21:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是英雄\N{\b0\fs12}I'm not a hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.45,0:22:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.54,0:22:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我根本就不是什麼英雄\N{\b0\fs12}I am the furthest thing from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.10,0:22:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我是塔爾•莎菲爾\N{\b0\fs12}I am "Ta-er Sah-fer."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.04,0:22:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我的新名字\N{\b0\fs12}That was my new name.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.99,0:22:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,因為曾經的那個女人\N{\b0\fs12}Because the woman that I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.66,0:22:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,曾經的那個女孩\N{\b0\fs12}the girl that I was,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.58,0:22:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,已經不見了\N{\b0\fs12}was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會假裝我和你有過\N{\b0\fs12}I'm not going to pretend that I've been through
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.44,0:22:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,同樣的經歷\N{\b0\fs12}anything that you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.50,0:22:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,去年我學到的一件事\N{\b0\fs12}One thing that I've learned in the past year
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.54,0:22:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,就是我們的經歷\N{\b0\fs12}is that these things...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.96,0:22:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不會擊垮我們\N{\b0\fs12}they don't break us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.85,0:22:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他們造就了我們\N{\b0\fs12}They make us who we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.71,0:22:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,而我...已經無可救藥了\N{\b0\fs12}And what I am... is irredeemable.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.84,0:22:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你剛剛說的是什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What was that word you said before?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,塔爾•莎菲爾\N{\b0\fs12}Ta-er Sah-fer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.74,0:22:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼意思\N{\b0\fs12}What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.71,0:22:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,意思是""金絲雀"."\N{\b0\fs12}It means "The Canary."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.59,0:23:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你早就喪失了本性\N{\b0\fs12}If you're so far gone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.52,0:23:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,而且無可救藥\N{\b0\fs12}and so irredeemable...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.45,0:23:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼會有這麼美麗的名字呢\N{\b0\fs12}then why would they know you by such a beautiful name?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.48,0:23:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利  奧利\N{\b0\fs12}Ollie! Ollie!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.71,0:23:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利  奧利  奧利  謝天謝地\N{\b0\fs12}Ollie, Ollie, Ollie! Thank God!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.12,0:23:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利  奧利\N{\b0\fs12}Ollie, Ollie...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.39,0:23:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我來\N{\b0\fs12}Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.70,0:23:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,來  跟我來\N{\b0\fs12}All right, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.26,0:23:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,這個潛艇就在貨船旁邊\N{\b0\fs12}The sub is right alongside the freighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.51,0:23:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你遊過去就可以了\N{\b0\fs12}You just need to swim, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.92,0:23:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\b0\fs12}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.91,0:23:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼還不走\N{\b0\fs12}OK, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.31,0:24:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我還不能走\N{\b0\fs12}I can't leave yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.33,0:24:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利  走吧\N{\b0\fs12}Ollie, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.33,0:24:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-解藥  -不\N{\b0\fs12}- The cure. - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.20,0:24:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能把斯萊德留下\N{\b0\fs12}I can't--I can't leave Slade behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.27,0:24:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能  就這麼丟棄他\N{\b0\fs12}I'm not just going to-- I'm not just going to write him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.12,0:24:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是我們給他打的米拉庫魯\N{\b0\fs12}We injected him with the Mirakuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.35,0:24:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是我打的  奧利\N{\b0\fs12}But it was me-- Ollie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.85,0:24:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我為了你放棄了莎朵\N{\b0\fs12}I chose you over Shado.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.51,0:24:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我  我只想回家\N{\b0\fs12}I--I just--I just want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.08,0:24:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想見到我的家人  奧利\N{\b0\fs12}I just want to see my family, Ollie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.92,0:24:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想死\N{\b0\fs12}Please, I don't want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.84,0:24:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧  求你了\N{\b0\fs12}Come on, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.92,0:24:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我必須這麼做\N{\b0\fs12}I need to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.56,0:24:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我要救回我的朋友\N{\b0\fs12}I need to save my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.87,0:24:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我至少得試一試\N{\b0\fs12}I need to at least try.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.92,0:24:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,到潛艇裡去\N{\b0\fs12}Get to the sub.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.68,0:24:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,保護自己\N{\b0\fs12}Get safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.74,0:24:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有你我就不去了\N{\b0\fs12}Not without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.14,0:24:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉\N{\b0\fs12}Sara...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.12,0:24:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\b0\fs12}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.87,0:24:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是爸爸\N{\b0\fs12}It's dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.44,0:24:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\b0\fs12}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.09,0:24:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾  你在哪裡\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel, baby, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.20,0:24:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,55街和阿爾弗雷德路口  這有幾個路障\N{\b0\fs12}55th and Alfred-- there were a few roadblocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.00,0:24:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧\N{\b0\fs12}But you're OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.70,0:25:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事  莎拉和我在一起\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah. Sara's with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.40,0:25:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好  你們兩個都待在原地\N{\b0\fs12}Right. Ok. Listen, stay there, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.37,0:25:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我馬上過去\N{\b0\fs12}I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.26,0:25:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-我能自己走  -他在哪裡\N{\b0\fs12}- I can walk. - Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.83,0:25:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,手機定位顯示他在500尺半徑以內\N{\b0\fs12}The cell phone GPS says he should be within a 500-foot radius.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.16,0:25:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我打給他\N{\b0\fs12}I'll call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.40,0:25:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪裡\N{\b0\fs12}Hey, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.68,0:25:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我們到了  你在哪  按下喇叭\N{\b0\fs12}We're here, where are you? Honk your horn.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.01,0:25:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好  等下\N{\b0\fs12}Cool. Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.46,0:25:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  我看到你的腳了\N{\b0\fs12}Wait! I can see your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.96,0:25:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你就在我車旁了\N{\b0\fs12}You're standing right outside my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.11,0:25:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是我們\N{\b0\fs12}That's not us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.56,0:25:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.52,0:25:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,東西沒了\N{\b0\fs12}It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.92,0:26:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,當前情勢非常緊張\N{\b0\fs12}The situation has intensified
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.90,0:26:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,當局正在全力控制\N{\b0\fs12}as officials struggle to contain
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.05,0:26:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這次前所未見的對我市的攻擊\N{\b0\fs12}this historic assault gripping our city.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.22,0:26:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,威爾遜先生  這是你要的東西嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Mr. Wilson, is this what you're looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.25,0:26:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,對  就是這個\N{\b0\fs12}Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.91,0:26:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我剛跟星級實驗室的西斯科通過電話\N{\b0\fs12}I just got off the phone with Cisco at S.T.A.R. Labs...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.88,0:26:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他們送過來的是全部的解藥\N{\b0\fs12}The cure they sent us was all they had.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.51,0:26:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他們用完了我們給的米拉庫魯\N{\b0\fs12}And they used all the Mirakuru that we gave them,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.55,0:26:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他們沒辦法再做了\N{\b0\fs12}so they can't make more.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.56,0:26:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有解藥我們就沒法阻止斯萊德的人\N{\b0\fs12}We can't stop Slade's men without the cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.54,0:26:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我們會找到其他方法的\N{\b0\fs12}We'll find another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.40,0:26:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有其他方法\N{\b0\fs12}There is no other way!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.97,0:26:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,狄格爾  鑄造廠被占領了\N{\b0\fs12}Diggle, the foundry's been compromised
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.42,0:26:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我們得把羅伊救出來\N{\b0\fs12}and we need to get Roy out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.64,0:26:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在就去\N{\b0\fs12}I'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.36,0:27:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  費利西蒂\N{\b0\fs12}I didn't know, Felicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.07,0:27:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,五年前  我和現在完全不同\N{\b0\fs12}Five years ago, I was a completely different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.33,0:27:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我從來...\N{\b0\fs12}And I had...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.51,0:27:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道竟然會...\N{\b0\fs12}no idea that something like this was even...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.07,0:27:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,發生這種事  我想像不到\N{\b0\fs12}possible. I couldn't have imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.63,0:27:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你和狄格爾找我回星城的時候\N{\b0\fs12}When you and Diggle brought me back to Starling City,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.15,0:27:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我對我自己發誓  絕對不會\N{\b0\fs12}I made a vow to myself that I would never let anything
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.42,0:27:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,讓爆炸慘劇之類的事再次發生\N{\b0\fs12}like the undertaking happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.43,0:27:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,現在發生的一切都不是你的錯\N{\b0\fs12}What's happening now is not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.57,0:27:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不  這是我的錯\N{\b0\fs12}Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.64,0:27:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我辜負了這座城市\N{\b0\fs12}I have failed this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.15,0:27:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,辜負了姚飛\N{\b0\fs12}Yao Fei.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.52,0:27:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,莎朵  湯米\N{\b0\fs12}Shado. Tommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.82,0:27:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我父親  我母親\N{\b0\fs12}My father, my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.12,0:27:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想緬懷這些人\N{\b0\fs12}All that I have ever wanted to do is honor those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.94,0:27:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就要繼續戰鬥下去\N{\b0\fs12}You honor the dead by fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.74,0:27:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你的戰鬥還沒有結束\N{\b0\fs12}And you are not done fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.19,0:27:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,馬爾科姆•梅林\N{\b0\fs12}Malcolm Merlyn,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.91,0:28:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,伯爵  同步信號之王\N{\b0\fs12}the Count, the Clock King,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.65,0:28:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,三合會  每一個想要傷害這座城市的人\N{\b0\fs12}The Triad--everyone who is trying to hurt this city,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.68,0:28:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,都被你阻止了\N{\b0\fs12}you stopped them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.52,0:28:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你也會阻止斯萊德的\N{\b0\fs12}And you will stop Slade.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.94,0:28:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-我不知道該怎麼做  -我也不知道\N{\b0\fs12}- I don't know how. - Neither do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.97,0:28:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但我知道兩件事\N{\b0\fs12}But I do know two things.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.93,0:28:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是一個人在戰鬥\N{\b0\fs12}You are not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.96,0:28:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我相信你能做到\N{\b0\fs12}And I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.96,0:28:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸在哪  他現在應該到了\N{\b0\fs12}Where's dad? He should be here by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.13,0:28:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你應該去個更有利的位置\N{\b0\fs12}You should get to a better vantage point.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.06,0:28:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,來人啊  救命啊\N{\b0\fs12}Somebody help! Please, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.63,0:28:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,待在這別動\N{\b0\fs12}Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.32,0:28:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,來人啊  救命啊\N{\b0\fs12}Someone help! Please help!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.15,0:28:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,救命啊\N{\b0\fs12}Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.43,0:28:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,救命\N{\b0\fs12}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.91,0:29:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我女兒還在裡面  我救不了她\N{\b0\fs12}My daughter is still inside, I couldn't get to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.11,0:29:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,別去  太危險了\N{\b0\fs12}Don't, it's too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.96,0:29:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-勞蕾爾  -爸爸\N{\b0\fs12}- Laurel! - Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.44,0:29:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你受傷了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.78,0:29:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有  我沒事  我還好\N{\b0\fs12}No, I'm fine. I'm OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.76,0:29:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,警員DC-52呼叫總部  請回覆\N{\b0\fs12}Delta Charlie 52 to central, copy!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.86,0:29:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,警員DC-52呼叫總部  請回覆\N{\b0\fs12}Delta Charlie 52 to central, copy!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.72,0:29:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,警員DC-52呼叫總部  請立即回覆\N{\b0\fs12}Delta Charlie 52 to central, please copy me, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.02,0:29:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-警員DC-52呼叫總部  -爸爸\N{\b0\fs12}- Delta Charlie 52 to central... - Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.74,0:29:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,她沒事\N{\b0\fs12}She's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.60,0:29:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那是誰\N{\b0\fs12}Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.84,0:30:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她是金絲雀\N{\b0\fs12}That's the Canary.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.29,0:30:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭  求你了  跟我走\N{\b0\fs12}Thea, please, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.23,0:30:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想跟你有關係\N{\b0\fs12}I don't want anything to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.39,0:30:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我根本不想見到你\N{\b0\fs12}I don't want to even see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.08,0:30:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,躲在我身後\N{\b0\fs12}Stay behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.29,0:30:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒有箭了\N{\b0\fs12}You're out of arrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.55,0:30:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你身上還有\N{\b0\fs12}You're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.19,0:30:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.67,0:30:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你的電話\N{\b0\fs12}this is your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.56,0:30:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}塞巴斯蒂安•布拉德\N來電
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.05,0:31:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你想怎麼樣\N{\b0\fs12}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.98,0:31:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,和你想的一樣  奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}Same thing you do, Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.53,0:31:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,趁還來得及  拯救這座城市\N{\b0\fs12}To save this city before it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.54,0:31:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,已經來不及了\N{\b0\fs12}It's already too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.02,0:31:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德•威爾遜的事被你說中了\N{\b0\fs12}You were right about Slade Wilson.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.74,0:31:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前應該聽你的\N{\b0\fs12}I should have listened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.01,0:31:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但我已經來了  我能幫助你\N{\b0\fs12}But I'm here now and I can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.65,0:31:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我憑什麼相信你\N{\b0\fs12}Why should I trust you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.18,0:31:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,因為  奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}Because, Oliver...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.91,0:31:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我有米拉庫魯的解藥\N{\b0\fs12}I have the Mirakuru cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.56,0:31:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的毒藥能讓他昏迷多長時間\N{\b0\fs12}How much venom do we have to keep him under?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.71,0:31:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,大約兩個小時\N{\b0\fs12}Two hours, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.64,0:31:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\b0\fs12}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.74,0:31:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你陪著羅伊\N{\b0\fs12}I need you to stay with Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.21,0:31:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\b0\fs12}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.13,0:31:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗  約翰\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver, John...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.03,0:31:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我多一句嘴\N{\b0\fs12}maybe this is obvious,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.06,0:31:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你們確定這不是圈套嗎\N{\b0\fs12}but are we sure this isn't a trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.73,0:31:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不確定\N{\b0\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.94,0:32:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我得說一句  要是你們不能活著回來\N{\b0\fs12}I'm just saying, if you guys don't come back alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.54,0:32:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我會非常生氣的\N{\b0\fs12}I'm going to be really pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.42,0:32:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我小時候經常被噩夢困擾\N{\b0\fs12}As a young boy, I was plagued by nightmares.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.48,0:32:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,每天晚上我都會驚醒\N{\b0\fs12}Every night, I would wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.47,0:32:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,渾身冒冷汗  感到害怕和孤獨\N{\b0\fs12}in a cold sweat, frightened and alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.16,0:32:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直忘不掉我父親那張臉\N{\b0\fs12}It was my father's face that haunted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.39,0:32:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是他在我眼中的樣子\N{\b0\fs12}And this is how I saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.35,0:32:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,簡直就是絕望的化身\N{\b0\fs12}The embodiment of desperation and despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.72,0:32:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我做這個面具是為了克服我的恐懼\N{\b0\fs12}I made this mask to conquer my fears.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.68,0:32:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,提醒自己為什麼要戰鬥\N{\b0\fs12}And remind myself why I fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.31,0:32:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是每一天\N{\b0\fs12}every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.96,0:33:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,都要給這座城市最絕望的人一個機會\N{\b0\fs12}to give this city's most desperate a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.97,0:33:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗  我只是想幫助別人\N{\b0\fs12}All I ever wanted to do was help people, Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.03,0:33:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就拿出實際行動來\N{\b0\fs12}Then help me believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.61,0:33:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,解藥在哪裡\N{\b0\fs12}Where is the cure?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.62,0:33:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德•威爾遜在兌現\N{\b0\fs12}Slade Wilson will not rest
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.34,0:33:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他對你的承諾之前  絕不會罷休\N{\b0\fs12}until he honors the promise that he made you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.19,0:33:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我們實力相當  他很難殺死我\N{\b0\fs12}I won't be so easy to kill once we level the playing field.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.51,0:33:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他還不想殺你\N{\b0\fs12}He's not interested in killing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.47,0:33:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,除非他已經奪走了一切\N{\b0\fs12}Not until he's taken away
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.54,0:33:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你所愛的人和物\N{\b0\fs12}everything and everyone you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.88,0:33:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他殺死我母親後\N{\b0\fs12}After he murdered my mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.04,0:33:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他說還有一個人要死\N{\b0\fs12}he said one more person had to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.80,0:33:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是你最愛的人\N{\b0\fs12}Whoever you love the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.98,0:33:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你能用這個打敗他\N{\b0\fs12}I hope you can beat him with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.80,0:33:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,為了我們所有人\N{\b0\fs12}For all our sakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.44,0:33:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,等這一切都結束了  我向你保證\N{\b0\fs12}And when this is over, I promise you...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.54,0:33:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我會盡我所能  重建星城\N{\b0\fs12}I will do everything in my power to rebuild Starling City.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.28,0:34:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我不僅會讓它恢復原貌\N{\b0\fs12}And I won't just make it what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.71,0:34:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,還會讓它變得更好\N{\b0\fs12}I will make it better.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.75,0:34:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,就像我一直計劃的那樣\N{\b0\fs12}Like I always planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.18,0:34:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的以為\N{\b0\fs12}You really think...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.53,0:34:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,在發生了這一切之後\N{\b0\fs12}after everything that's happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.44,0:34:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,就憑你的這些所作所為\N{\b0\fs12}after what you've done,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.41,0:34:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,人們還會繼續讓你當市長嗎\N{\b0\fs12}that they'll still let you be mayor?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.53,0:34:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼不\N{\b0\fs12}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.13,0:34:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他們只知道我在盡力挽救這座城市\N{\b0\fs12}No one knows that I've done anything except try to save this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.66,0:34:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你告訴別人我那面具的事\N{\b0\fs12}And if you tell anyone about my mask,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.29,0:34:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我也會把你的事抖出來\N{\b0\fs12}I will tell them about yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.81,0:34:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,做好你該做的事  塞巴斯蒂安\N{\b0\fs12}Do what you have to, Sebastian.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.18,0:34:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我得回去了\N{\b0\fs12}I got to get back to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.22,0:34:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你們沒事吧\N{\b0\fs12}Hey. Are you guys OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.51,0:34:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你有沒有事\N{\b0\fs12}Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.60,0:34:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,簡直難以置信  一個戴面具的金髮女子\N{\b0\fs12}You wouldn't believe it-- a blonde in a mask
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.84,0:34:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,抱著個孩子沖出了大火熊熊的建築物\N{\b0\fs12}ran out of a burning building with a kid in her arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.45,0:34:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太勇敢了  那個女人是個英雄\N{\b0\fs12}It was the bravest thing I've ever seen. That woman's a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.52,0:35:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你給他了對不對\N{\b0\fs12}You gave it to him, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.81,0:35:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得有這個必要\N{\b0\fs12}I did what I thought was necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.91,0:35:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不用擔心  我會跟斯萊德說\N{\b0\fs12}Don't worry, I'll tell Slade.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.12,0:35:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他手裡還有解藥嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Does he still have the cure?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.21,0:35:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有\N{\b0\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.68,0:35:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德  你背叛了...\N{\b0\fs12}Slade, you betrayed--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.06,0:35:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,永別了  布拉德先生\N{\b0\fs12}Good-bye, Mr. Blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.21,0:35:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我愛過這座城市\N{\b0\fs12}I loved this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.77,0:36:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼所有秘方都有顏色\N{\b0\fs12}Why does every secret formula have to be a color?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.69,0:36:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,歷史悠久的無色都哪裡去了\N{\b0\fs12}Whatever happened to good, old-fashioned clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.29,0:36:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我們給斯萊德的戰士注射這個...\N{\b0\fs12}All right, so if we inject one of Slade's soldiers with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.52,0:36:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,根據星級實驗室的研究\N{\b0\fs12}According to S.T.A.R. Labs,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.40,0:36:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這個會抵消米拉庫魯的藥效\N{\b0\fs12}it will counteract the effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.40,0:36:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,前提是他們的配方正確\N{\b0\fs12}Assuming they got the recipe right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.40,0:36:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我們得先測試一下\N{\b0\fs12}We need to test it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.83,0:36:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\b0\fs12}We can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.05,0:36:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,要把羅伊當做實驗小白鼠嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Treat Roy like some kind of lab rat?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.43,0:36:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,費利西蒂\N{\b0\fs12}Felicity...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.30,0:36:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,要是不起作用呢\N{\b0\fs12}What if it doesn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.02,0:36:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,要是把他害死了呢\N{\b0\fs12}What if it kills him?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.68,0:36:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,要是他醒來把我們殺了呢\N{\b0\fs12}What if he wakes up and kills us?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.83,0:36:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我們總得想辦法知道\N{\b0\fs12}We need to know. One way or the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.24,0:36:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,去把另一扇門關上\N{\b0\fs12}Go lock the other door.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.98,0:36:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\b0\fs12}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.43,0:37:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉  艾沃的保險箱在哪裡\N{\b0\fs12}Sara, where does Ivo keep his safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.69,0:37:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,在...  他的書邊上\N{\b0\fs12}It's, uh, by his books.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.16,0:37:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.66,0:37:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你找什麼呢  小子  這個嗎\N{\b0\fs12}What are you looking for, kid? This?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.42,0:37:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,蘭斯警探\N{\b0\fs12}Detective Lance.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.30,0:37:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.03,0:37:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了\N{\b0\fs12}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.56,0:37:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了\N{\b0\fs12}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.69,0:37:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,現在直播的是\N{\b0\fs12}You're watching live footage
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.52,0:37:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一支護航軍隊\N{\b0\fs12}of an army convoy arriving
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.04,0:37:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,抵達星城外郊準備恢復城市秩序\N{\b0\fs12}on the outskirts of the city to restore order.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.80,0:37:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,裝甲部隊終於來了\N{\b0\fs12}Looks like the cavalry's here, finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.74,0:37:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-可能吧  -什麼意思\N{\b0\fs12}- Maybe. - What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.24,0:38:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他們正在占領大橋和隧道\N{\b0\fs12}Well, they're taking up positions in the bridges and tunnels.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.55,0:38:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那是進城的唯一方法\N{\b0\fs12}Well, those are the only ways into the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.25,0:38:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,對  也是出城的唯一方法\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, and the only ways out.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.34,0:38:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我一個做軍事情報的哥們\N{\b0\fs12}A buddy of mine in military intelligence
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.85,0:38:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,曾經跟我說軍隊並不總是軍隊\N{\b0\fs12}once told me the army isn't always the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.82,0:38:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,但顯然是軍方\N{\b0\fs12}But it's clearly the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.89,0:38:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,看他們的卡車  制服\N{\b0\fs12}The trucks, the uniforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.28,0:38:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但是最近的軍事基地在市政局紀念廳\N{\b0\fs12}Except the nearest army base is at Monument Point,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.00,0:38:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,離這裡有300英里遠\N{\b0\fs12}which is 300 miles from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.37,0:38:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他們怎麼會這麼快就到星城了呢\N{\b0\fs12}So how could they mobilize to Starling City so fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.27,0:38:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  如果不是軍隊\N{\b0\fs12}OK. So if that isn't the army,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.22,0:38:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那到底是誰\N{\b0\fs12}who the hell are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.18,0:38:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起\N{\b0\fs12}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.16,0:39:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我下不了手\N{\b0\fs12}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.64,0:39:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是蘭斯  警探\N{\b0\fs12}It's Lance. Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.76,0:39:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-他在嗎  -在\N{\b0\fs12}- Are you near him? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.59,0:39:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-你那邊有電視嗎  -有\N{\b0\fs12}- Are you near a TV? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.07,0:39:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,打開\N{\b0\fs12}Turn it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.93,0:39:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼知道我這個號碼的\N{\b0\fs12}How did you get this number?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.93,0:39:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,阿曼達  你在幹什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Amanda. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.95,0:39:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我不懂你的意思  奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}I'm not sure what you mean, Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.68,0:39:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,阿曼達  那支部隊占領了星城的出口...\N{\b0\fs12}Amanda, the troops taking up position at the city's exits--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.64,0:39:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他們不是軍方的人  是超能力聯合調查組\N{\b0\fs12}They're not army, they're A.R.G.U.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.90,0:39:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是你的人  所以你告訴我你到底想幹什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Those are your men. So you tell me what you're up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.04,0:39:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,阿曼達\N{\b0\fs12}Amanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.62,0:39:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德的追隨者明顯\N{\b0\fs12}Slade's followers are a clear
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.23,0:39:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是我們目前的威脅  我不能讓他們\N{\b0\fs12}and present danger. I cannot allow them
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.35,0:39:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,逃出星城  得控制住他們...\N{\b0\fs12}to escape the city. They need to be contained...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.68,0:39:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不惜任何手段\N{\b0\fs12}by any means necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.64,0:39:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能這樣做\N{\b0\fs12}You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.64,0:40:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,現在正有一架無人機\N{\b0\fs12}There's a drone en route
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.75,0:40:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,帶著六枚GBU/43-B炸彈過去\N{\b0\fs12}carrying six GBU/43-B bombs,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.48,0:40:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,火力足以將星城夷為平地\N{\b0\fs12}enough fire power to level the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.88,0:40:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,星城裡還有50多萬平民呢\N{\b0\fs12}There are over half a million people in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.61,0:40:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,57萬6千人\N{\b0\fs12}576,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.53,0:40:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他們都是無辜的\N{\b0\fs12}None of whom deserve to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.59,0:40:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但我也得為其他城市的人考慮\N{\b0\fs12}But I have to think about the people in every city.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.08,0:40:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你說過米拉庫魯會讓人變得堅不可摧\N{\b0\fs12}You once told me that Mirakuru made a man virtually unstoppable.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.42,0:40:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我不馬上結束這件事\N{\b0\fs12}What could happen to this country,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.92,0:40:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那對我們國家\N{\b0\fs12}this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.67,0:40:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,還有整個世界會有什麼後果\N{\b0\fs12}if I don't end this here and now?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.87,0:40:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,聽我說\N{\b0\fs12}Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.59,0:40:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我有解藥\N{\b0\fs12}I have the cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.58,0:40:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以阻止斯萊德和他的人\N{\b0\fs12}I can stop Slade and his men.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.33,0:40:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,萬一失敗了呢  我不能冒這個險  奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}I can't take the chance you'll fail, Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.15,0:40:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,阿曼達  求你多給我點時間\N{\b0\fs12}Amanda, I just need more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.94,0:40:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起\N{\b0\fs12}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.06,0:40:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,只能到黎明之前\N{\b0\fs12}You have until dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.59,0:40:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,否則星城就會成為一片廢墟\N{\b0\fs12}And then Starling City is a crater.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.37,0:41:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你想開槍的話\N{\b0\fs12}If you're going to use that,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.19,0:41:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,記得關掉保險\N{\b0\fs12}you'll want to click the safety off.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.31,0:41:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我會開槍的\N{\b0\fs12}I'll shoot you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.61,0:41:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我會的\N{\b0\fs12}I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.95,0:41:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以從你眼中看到\N{\b0\fs12}I can see it in your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.01,0:41:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我的眼睛\N{\b0\fs12}My eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.61,0:41:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你的眼睛跟我的一樣\N{\b0\fs12}They're just like mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.77,0:41:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,雙眼中都充滿了痛苦和憤怒\N{\b0\fs12}Both of them filled with pain and anger,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.75,0:41:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我們愛的人都被搶走了\N{\b0\fs12}because those we loved were ripped from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.39,0:41:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我失去了我的名字  我妻子\N{\b0\fs12}I lost my name, my wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.20,0:41:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,湯米\N{\b0\fs12}Tommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.18,0:41:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,閉嘴\N{\b0\fs12}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.61,0:41:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你是這個世界上我唯一的親人了\N{\b0\fs12}You're all I have left in this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.38,0:41:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你也失去了一切\N{\b0\fs12}and you've lost everything, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.71,0:41:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭\N{\b0\fs12}Thea.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.03,0:41:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你還有父親\N{\b0\fs12}But you still have a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.14,0:41:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你還有...\N{\b0\fs12}You still have...
